Single: Stripped
From the album: "For the Masses" (Depeche Mode Tribute-Album)
Info: The video contains footage from the film "Olympia - Festival of the Nations", which were shot during the Olympic Games 1936 by the controversial director Leni Riefenstahl.

For the Depeche Mode Tribute Album "For the Masses" Rammstein recorded a cover version of the song STRIPPED at Hamburger Vox Klangstudio (January 27th - February 1st)
